# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __ipow__, __ilshift__, __irshift__ across all 5 pathlib subjects
#
# 5 classes x 3 methods = 15 rows.
# All values are false; pathlib defines no in-place exponentiation or bitwise
# shift operators. Path objects are filesystem path abstractions; arithmetic
# and bitwise augmented-assignment operators are not part of the path protocol.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

